If your goal is **just to test with minimal changes**, then don't add the `configurations.all` block or the Jackson BOM.

Just make these minimal changes.

## Option 1 (Smallest change)

Replace:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind'
```

with:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-core:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.14.2'
```

That's it. No other changes.

