## Even smaller change

Since you already had these lines commented:

```gradle
// implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda:2.12.3'
// implementation group: 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core', name: 'jackson-databind', version: '2.17.2'
// implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.15.2'
```

You can simply replace your current two lines with:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.14.2'
```

I would also add:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-core:2.14.2'
```

because Jackson modules should stay on the same version.

